<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="W" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Wager2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Wager,</orth> vb. to bet: <cit><quote>and w. on your heads,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 4.7.135" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 7, 135</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ant 2.5.16" default="NO" valid="yes">Ant. II, 5, 16</bibl>. <cit><quote>hath --ed with him six Barbary horses,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 5.2.154" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. V, 2, 154</bibl></cit> (Ff <emph>waged</emph>). <bibl n="shak. cym 5.5.182" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 5, 182</bibl> (later Ff <emph>waged</emph>). <cit><quote>I durst to w. she is honest,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 4.2.12" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. IV, 2, 12</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. per 5.1.43" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. V, 1, 43</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>